Description: GHC toolchain installer
 GHCup is the main installer for the general purpose language Haskell.
 .
 It manages installation of GHC (Glasgow Haskell Compiler), HLS (Haskell
 Language Server), cabal-install (Haskell build tool), and Stack (Haskell
 build tool).
 .
 GHCup can install multiple versions of each tool and allows switching
 between them easily. It supports various platforms including Linux,
 macOS, FreeBSD, and Windows.
